name: Maximal Galaxy Tee
description:
High super premium quality tee with the Maximal Clothing Galaxy Logo Print.

100% cotton and weighing 200gsm.

"The preshrunk fabric ensures this t-shirt will last and provide hassle-free at-home washing with minimum shrinkage wash after wash. "

"Added comfort for the wearer is provided by twin needle stitching throughout the garment, and a taped neck. These features offer increased durability so your t-shirt will last, too. "

Available in white.

Postage costs: £3 for customers from the UK. 
£6 for customers outside the UK.

For best results please wash at 30° and do not tumble dry.
